==Arabic==
===Etymology===
From the root verb {{ARchar|[[نظر]]}} {{IPAchar|(náʐara)}}, to [[perceive]] with the eyes.

===Noun 1===
'''{{ARchar|منظر}}''' {{IPAchar|(mánʐar)}} {{m}}, {{ARchar|[[مناظر]]}} {{IPAchar|(mánāʐir)}} {{p}}

# [[sight]]
# [[view]], [[panorama]]
# [[looks]], [[appearance]], [[aspect]]
# [[prospect]], [[outlook]], [[perspective]]
#''(photography)'' [[object]]
# [[scene]] ''(of a play)''
# [[spectacle]]
# stage [[setting]], [[set]], [[scenery]]
# [[lookout]], [[watchtower]]

===Noun 2===
'''{{ARchar|منظر}}''' {{IPAchar|(mínʐar)}} {{m}}

# pair of [[eyeglasses]], [[spectacles]]
# [[telescope]]

